name: Fleur Noir Black Filigree Pendant with Turquoise and Double Red Leather Cord Necklace
description:
A beautiful large unique vintage German plastic filigree pendant is combined with two faceted turquoise briolettes and a double red leather cord. Gorgeous focal pendant necklace makes this a "must have". 

Pendant measures 54mm. 
Necklace length is 16 inches.

name: Starlight Vintage Silverware and Swarovski Crystal Handmade Charm Bracelet
description:
Everyone needs a little radiance now and then. This beautiful recycled/upcycled bracelet features vintage patterned silverware handles. A blue swarovski crystal and a decorative bali sterling silver bead are the focal charms at the front of this bracelet. A large sterling silver lobster clasp at the back makes it easy to put on and take off. Very well made and gorgeous!

Fits 7 1/2 inches

For a custom fit...
Leave your exact wrist size upon checking out in the message to seller box. 

*bracelet is made from upcycled/recycled silverplate silverware. 


Please note that pictures are deliberately taken to show detail in my pieces. Therefore, be aware that some jewelry will look larger in the pictures than it actually is in real life.

Also, keep in mind, colors may vary from monitor to monitor. Slight irregularities, color variations and inclusions are natural characteristics and uniqueness in the gemstones and pearls that are used in my jewelry collection

name: Tropical Blue Chalcedony Stone and White Pearl Cluster Sterling Silver Earrings
description:
Vibrant tropical blue faceted fan shaped AAA chalcedony are wire wrapped in sterling silver topped with tiny 2mm white pearl charms. Absolutely stunning and beautiful!

Earring length is 1 1/4 inches.

Chalcedony stones are 12mm x10mm.

name: Rose Quartz Gemstone Wire Wrapped Flower Pendant Handmade Necklace
description:
Beautiful faceted pale pink briolettes are hand wire wrapped into a spring flower of sparkle. This handmade pendant dangles from a 16 inch sterling silver chain. Gorgeous to go with any color in your wardrobe dressed up or down.

Pendant measures: 25mm
Necklace length: 16 inches

Earrings length is 1 1/2 inches, lightweight and comfortable to wear.
